aquifer. We expect our approach to deliver significant environmental and socio-economic co-benefits to coastal and inland communities and ecosystems, many of which are already suffering from the effects of land degradation and a lack of investment. Solutions are scalable and standalone, however when combined, their synergy greatly increases benefits on a regional scale.
